        <p class="govuk-body">If you are not a UK citizen you are unlikely to be eligible for a student loan. Find out what <a href="https://getintoteaching.education.gov.uk/non-uk-teachers/fees-and-funding-for-non-uk-trainees">financial support is available to people from outside the UK.</a></p>
    </div>
