    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Financial support from the training provider</h4>

  <p class="govuk-body">Students who have previously graduated from an undergraduate course at the University of Roehampton may be eligible for an alumni discount amounting to £1500.</p>
  
   <p class="govuk-body">This discount will also be available to Roehampton alumnus undertaking a PGCE with QTS qualification with one of our school partners.</p>

    <p class="govuk-body">Please note that the previous course studied at the university must have been at a lower level (i.e. undergraduate and not Masters).</p>

  

